<section id="sect-Red_Hat_CloudForms-Scripting_Actions_in_CloudForms-Creating_a_Domain" remap="TID_41994">
	<title>Creating a Domain</title>
	 <procedure id="proc-Red_Hat_CloudForms-Scripting_Actions_in_CloudForms-Creating_a_Domain-To_Create_a_Domain">
		<title>To Create a Domain</title>
		 <step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Automate</guimenu><guisubmenu>Explorer</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. The default view is the Datastore.
			</para>

		</step>
		 <step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1847.png" format="PNG" />
					</imageobject>

				</inlinemediaobject>
				<guilabel>(Configuration)</guilabel>, then 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2365.png" format="PNG" />
					</imageobject>

				</inlinemediaobject>
				 <guilabel>(Add a New Domain)</guilabel>.
			</para>

		</step>
		 <step>
			<para>
				Type in a unique <guilabel>Name</guilabel> and <guilabel>Description</guilabel>. Choose if the Domain is <guilabel>Enabled</guilabel>.
			</para>

		</step>
		 <step>
			<para>
				Click <guilabel>Add</guilabel>.
			</para>

		</step>

	</procedure>
	 <formalpara id="form-Red_Hat_CloudForms-Scripting_Actions_in_CloudForms-Creating_a_Domain-Result">
		<title>Result:</title>
		 <para>
			The new domain is created.
		</para>

	</formalpara>
</section>

